                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial-card">
                    <div class="quote-icon">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--orange)"><path d="M6 17h3l2-4V7H5v6h3zm8 0h3l2-4V7h-6v6h3z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <p class="testimonial-text" data-i18n="testimonial3">"The e-learning modules delivered by learn2grow are easy-to-use, interactive, well structured and they cover all important topics and areas."</p>
                    <div class="testimonial-author-block">
                        <p class="testimonial-author">Learning & Development Manager</p>
                        <p class="testimonial-company">FMCG</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
