                    <h3 class="article-title" data-i18n="article3Title">ESG in Practice: Supporting Clients on Their Sustainability Journey</h3>
                    <p class="article-excerpt" data-i18n="article3Excerpt">Real change within an organization starts with people and their understanding of new challenges.</p>
                    <a href="/esg-in-practice" class="read-more-link" data-i18n="readMore">
                        Read more
                        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="/insights" class="cta-orange-rounded" data-i18n="readAll">
                Read All Insights
